trong>FINACE CHAIRMAN (ACT IN PLACE)</strong><br>Colonel Thanapol Bhakdibhumi</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontFamily\":\"Rubik\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-rubik-font-family has-custom-font\" style=\"font-family:Rubik\"><strong>VICE CHAIRMAN</strong><br>Mr. Pijak Chantaviroj</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"fontFamily\":\"Rubik\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"wp-block-heading has-rubik-font-family has-custom-font\" style=\"font-family:Rubik\">8. MEDICAL ADVISORY BOARD</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontFamily\":\"Rubik\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-rubik-font-family has-custom-font\" style=\"font-family:Rubik\"><strong>CHAIRMAN&nbsp;</strong><br>Mr. Pholritti Phanphakdee</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontFamily\":\"Rubik\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-rubik-font-family has-custom-font\" style=\"font-family:Rubik\"><strong>VICE CHAIRMAN</strong><br>Dr. Sitha Pongpiboon</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontFamily\":\"Rubik\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-rubik-font-family has-custom-font\" style=\"font-family:Rubik\"><strong>SECRETARY</strong><br>Col. Anupong Rodsai MD.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '173-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-10-21 21:49:21', '2024-10-21 21:49:21', '', 173, 'https://wbcmuaythai.com.mx/?p=242', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
